Class UserAppReviews

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.deprez.UserAppReviews

  • public class UserAppReviews
extends java.lang.Object
    The UserAppReviews class manages the list of UserAppReview plain java objects. It can sort the list and change anything about the list.
